    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a superlative example of high-revving Bavarian precision. The S54 straight-six engine is mechanically pristine, featuring a recently calibrated Double VANOS system and documented rod bearing replacement for long-term reliability. Power is delivered through a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory M-Variable limited-slip differential. The chassis integrity is absolute, with a reinforced rear subframe and a suspension setup that retains its original damping characteristics and bushing compliance. Finished in factory-correct paint with an interior featuring supple Nappa leather and zero bolster wear, this specimen is free of any electrolytic or mechanical degradation. It represents a turn-key investment for the discerning enthusiast who demands peak atmospheric performance.",
