    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! You have got to see this beauty. It\u2019s honestly like it just rolled off the showroom floor\u2014not a single scratch or a speck of dust anywhere! I\u2019ve babied this car since day one, and it still has that fresh, new-car feel and drives like an absolute dream. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s basically brand new without the brand new price tag, this is the one! I'd love for it to go to a great home, so come take it for a spin\u2014you\u2019re going to fall in love!",
      "price": 44500.0,
