    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offered is an investment-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) in pristine Alpine White. This example features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering peak torque with linear power delivery through six individual throttle bodies. The drivetrain is anchored by a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory M-Variable limited-slip differential. Mechanically, this chassis has been fastidiously maintained: the rod bearings have been replaced with treated shells, the VANOS system has been fully rebuilt with uprated seals, and the rear subframe has been proactively reinforced to ensure structural rigidity. The suspension retains its factory compliance but benefits from refreshed bushings and Bilstein dampers, ensuring optimal kinematic geometry and sharp turn-in response. The interior shows zero bolster wear on the Nappa leather, and the exterior retains its original factory clear coat with no signs of oxidation or road rash. A true analog masterpiece for the discerning driver.",
